body: I don't think anyone is particularly maintaining that code. For CIFAR-10 I would recommend looking at our [example in the official models](https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/official/resnet/cifar10_main.py) instead. As a plus, it also achieves much higher accuracy.
